490
00:17:49.027 --> 00:17:50.728
So just take a second to wallow in this.

491
00:17:50.761 --> 00:17:52.460
but then get cleaned up and get back out there. yeah?

492
00:17:52.493 --> 00:17:53.592
- Yeah.

493
00:18:00.625 --> 00:18:01.992
- Oh. you're too kind.

494
00:18:02.026 --> 00:18:03.859
