00:19:12.951 --> 00:19:15.451
This one time. this guy disassociated so hard

525
00:19:15.484 --> 00:19:16.718
he reported himself missing.

526
00:19:16.751 --> 00:19:18.584
- No. but this one's weird.

527
00:19:18.617 --> 00:19:20.851
Apple has a strong social media presence

528
00:19:20.884 --> 00:19:23.450
