- I see what's going on.

536
00:19:37.849 --> 00:19:38.982
You said she lives in your building?

537
00:19:39.016 --> 00:19:41.716
- Mm-hmm. - Classic move.

538
00:19:41.749 --> 00:19:43.448
You take the case near your house

539
