699
00:27:07.702 --> 00:27:09.535
I'm sorry!

700
00:27:09.568 --> 00:27:10.701
It's not what you think!

701
00:27:24.733 --> 00:27:26.799
- Okay. okay.

702
00:27:57.562 --> 00:27:59.963
