We're gonna go out the window.

735
00:29:29.519 --> 00:29:30.953
No. we're not.

736
00:29:30.986 --> 00:29:32.686
- I can hear you in there.

737
00:29:32.719 --> 00:29:34.085
Open the door. or we kick it in.

738
